description.3: The mighty Abomination rises! As S.H.I.E.L.D. investigates the crash site of a fallen meteor, they uncover an even greater horror in Bruce Banner' worst enemy. Will the Grey Hulk be an adequate match for this superior foe?
description.4: Storm and Jean Grey's friendship blossoms in ""First Friends!""
description.5: Frank Miller explores the push and pull nature of Kingpin and Daredevil's relationship. Vanessa Fisk represents all that the Kingpin holds dear; when the woman he loves is in grave danger, Fisk will act savagely to save her. All's fair in Love and War, and for Kingpin the saying's particularly true!
description.6: A giant, mechano-wolf demands Spider-Ham's intervention! But why is Dragon-Lassy to blame for this menace?
description.9: It's an all-out super-brawl! X-Factor, the New Exiles, Crimson Dynamo and more collide in this super-sized extravaganza from one of comic's greatest storytellers, Bob Layton!
description.10: The WCA face off with a whole gang of new super-villains - Quantum, Zzzax, and Halflife. And while they're busy trying to get these menaces under control, an older enemy of theirs makes an incredible return!
description.12: The New Mutants retaliate against Empath of the Hellions, following his emotional torment of Tom Corsi and Sharon Friedlander.
description.16: What do you do when a gang of super-villains gets together to make a lot of money out of crime? If you're Silver Sable, Inc., which makes its money catching crooks, you hire Spider-Man! But will even Spidey be enough to stop Hydroman, Speed Demon, the Beetle, Boomerang and the rampaging Rhino?
description.17: By popular demand, the villain you love to hate is back- Flag-Smasher! This time he's leading a band of terrorists who are holding a group of Americans hostage! How can Captain America save them before Flag-Smasher carries out his "Ultimatum"?
description.18: Daredevil deals with a new super hero, Madcap, who's as immune to injury as he is out of his mind!
description.19: Complications arise when the Vision attempts to merge Bruce Banner's body with the Hulk's.
description.20: Happy Hogan needs a loan from Tony Stark, but when he and the boxer he's been managing visit Tony, troubles erupts as it is discovered that Spymaster is in their midst! Who is Spymaster disguising himself as?
description.23: Our heroes are inside the 'Black Dome', where time moves at an accelerated pace and the people inside worship the FF as gods! Who could be behind such technology? And where is She-Hulk?
description.24: The fight between the X-Men and the Hellfire Club over the fate of Rachel Summers is interrupted when Nimrod descends upon them!
description.26: Luke Skywalker, Leia Organa, Han Solo, and Dani, together with a mixed team of commandos, including their new-found Imperial and Nagai allies are attacking the Tof-held world of Saijo, which just may unite the universe!
description.27: The First Appearance of the children of Vision and the Scarlet Witch -- it's the birth of Billy and Tommy!  It's what you've been waiting for! The Scarlet Witch and Vision introduce their new family. But will the mystical birth go off without a hitch?
description.29: Howard has finally hit the jackpot, winning a million dollars from a publishing sweepstakes! With the fame and fortune, Howard is a changed man and not for the better. Beverly doesn't agree with the new Howard the Duck and leaves him once again. Will Howard the Duck ever be loved again?
description.34: Disgraced reporter Winston Caribou is worshipped as a god at the Temple of the Golden Retriever, and Peter and the interns have the juicy lead!
description.35: Danny seeks the secret of the Dragon's Tale. The only one who can tell him is the fabled Old Master, a man marked for murder by a band of merciless ninjas sent by the evil Yellow Claw!
description.36: This is it! The all-out war concludes between the Eternals and the Deviants, and a few key Avengers will be brought into the fold!
description.37: Mockingbird encounters Kung Fu action of the lethal kind when she goes to get the straight scoop from Nick Fury about S.H.I.E.L.D.'s recent ominous doings, and instead runs straight into Razorfist, Shockwave and Zaran!
description.40: When Sam gets anxiety over his girlfriend Lila meeting his mother, he flies off the handle and accuses Lila of being a thief!
description.42: Captain America intervenes in Daredevil's battle with Nuke and finds out that the government has still been using the Super Soldier Program.
description.43: Two is better than one! Bruce Banner must merge back with the Hulk to save his life!
description.44: Morgana le Fae has possessed the sister of the werewolf by night! Can Iron Man stop her before she gets the body she's possessing into deep trouble? Guest starring the Werewolf by Night.
description.46: With a new deck of cards that will protect him from death and injury, Sundance ventures out with Thor to defeat Loki. Can this super duo reclaim the Apples of Idunn?
description.49: A giant dome of darkness has enveloped Central City- and She-Hulk is trapped inside! Can the FF save her from a violent fate?
description.52: Where is Spider-Man? It's the question on everyone's lips, as Peter Parker remains M.I.A. With her Wild Pack hospitalized, will Silver Sable be able to defeat Jack O' Lantern alone?
description.53: Scourge has slain 29 Marvel characters so far! His sights are now set on number 30 - Captain America!
description.54: Extra-hungry extra-terrestrial ""B.O."" has been devouring everything in sight, causing a nightmare for the Daily Beagle staff!
description.55: Will the Dreaming Celestial wake from its millennia-long slumber? Ghaur certainly hopes so, in the penultimate issue to the Eternals’ saga for Earth!
description.56: Only days away from giving birth, Wanda and Vizh make final preparations. Peter Parker makes an appearance, while Quicksilver slips into insanity!
description.63: While visiting her hometown, Dani Moonstar encounters her old frenemy Pat Roberts, who's involved in a terrible car accident. Can Danielle set their past differences aside to save her friend?
description.64: The truth of the three maidens will be revealed! Can Thor counteract Balder's ensorcellment? Meanwhile, in Midgard, Thug makes a discovery when he goes to see Ruby-a discovery that further fuels his hate for Thor...
description.66: The Thing is missing? The search for their newest member puts the West Coast Avengers on a collision course with Headlok!
description.67: The breakup of Crystal and Quicksilver. And this split leads hot-headed Pietro into an even greater frenzy!
description.69: Hog-zilla has kicked off a Japanese rampage, and only Peter Porker and the interns can slice up the monstrous swine!
description.70: A killer is on a rampage! How many more people will die before Power Man can stop him?
description.72: The God of Thunder guest stars in this chapter written by legendary Thor creator Walt Simonson! The Deviants’ master plan comes to full light, and Earth stands a slim to none chance at survival.
description.73: Is Flash Thompson the Hobgoblin? Peter Parker investigates. But while visiting Flash behind bars, Scourge makes his move against the NYPD! Spider-Man's not just taking on Scourge- Wraith shows up to get his revenge too!
description.74: While Kang gloats over his captive Avengers, the unengaged members attack. The team manages to flee the clutches of Kang, and convince Immortus to send them back to their rightful time and place.
description.75: Justice is served! When Captain America gets a tip that there's a change coming to the crime circuit, Steve Rogers investigates a series of murders within the criminal underworld . Find out who's behind it all when Captain America enters the snake pit!
description.76: The planet Zeltros has been conquered by two invading armies! The Zeltrons' only hope now is Luke Skywalker, the telepathic Space Bunnies and a dozen cowardly cockroaches!
description.77: Matt helps Karen kick her drug habit. Kingpin hires a deranged Super Soldier to go after Daredevil.
description.78: The Avengers and the Fantastic Four discover that the Hulk they are after is no longer connected to Bruce Banner- can they kill the beast given this new information?
description.79: Iron Man becomes involved with AIM's attempted takeover of a South American nation. The big question? Whose side is Shellhead on?
description.83: It's the FF vs. the Fuhrer! Will Nick Fury's ambitions of killing the leader of the Third Reich alter the world forever?
description.84: As Rachel's dark dreams become more and more vivid, Wolverine gets caught up in her psychic troubles.
description.90: The origins of Master Pandemonium are revealed!
description.92: Emma Frost calls in reinforcement…from Earth’s Mightiest Heroes! For the sake of his students’ return, Magneto and the Avengers do unholy battle!
description.93: An Asgardian has been slain! But not everything is as it seems and so Thor and the Warriors Three ride for Nornheim to uncover the truth. What will they find? Meanwhile, in Midgard, Thatcher is released from prison.
description.95: Ben begins to expose the Kingpin and accidentally puts his wife in danger in the process. Matt and Karen are finally re-united!
description.96: Bruce and Betty's honeymoon is less than magical when Bruce suddenly collapses on their cruise ship! The Hulk inches closer and closer to New Mexico. Can Doc Samson and the Hulkbusters hold down the base with Banner out of office?
description.97: Tony continues to work on the Stark Space Shuttle. Meanwhile, the Scientist Supreme of AIM infamy touches down on the West Coast!

0.text: Ricky's got a pen with a sample of experimental nerve gas inside, and he has no idea what he’s carrying -- so Dakota heads to Paris to find him.

2.text: Co-starring the Friendly Neighborhood Wall-Crawler! Top Dog and Joey are set on a mystery involving Spider-Man!

7.text: The droids babysit an alien baby whose parents' ship careens out of control and into a time warp.Then, they find themselves on Endor, interacting with Wicket and the other Ewoks!

8.text: The searing tale begun in Avengers Annual (1967) #15 concludes here! The traitor stands revealed! But not even both the Avengers and West Coast Avengers are prepared for the scope of the former Avenger's treachery!

9.text: It's an all-out super-brawl! X-Factor, the New Exiles, Crimson Dynamo and more collide in this super-sized extravaganza from one of comic's greatest storytellers, Bob Layton!

10.text: The WCA face off with a whole gang of new super-villains - Quantum, Zzzax, and Halflife. And while they're busy trying to get these menaces under control, an older enemy of theirs makes an incredible return!

11.text: Enter the All-New, All-Different Uncanny X-Men.  When a mutant is detected on Krakoa, the X-Men head out to investigate. When only Cyclops return, Professor X puts together a new team of X-Men!

12.text: The New Mutants retaliate against Empath of the Hellions, following his emotional torment of Tom Corsi and Sharon Friedlander.

13.text: Long live Balder, ruler of Asgard! Justin Peace has emerged from the timestream to undertake a vital mission but Thor doesn't take too kindly to time-traveling strangers in his neck of the woods. Plus, the emergence of the new Zaniac!

14.text: X-Force is called upon to clear up a mutant situation in Central Park in the midst of a media frenzy.

15.text: BREAKAWAY! It's Wasp and Paladin against The Grey Gargoyle! Meanwhile, supervillains are being sprung from prisons all over the country! Featuring Black Knight, Captain America, Captain Marvel, and Hercules!

31.text: The Ewoks journey to a hidden kingdom…underneath the sea!

32.text: The kids return to Earth just as the Fantastic Four are headed to Snarkworld to find them…!

33.text: While Dagger sightsees in Marseilles, Cloak gets to work trailing drug smugglers!

37.text: Mockingbird encounters Kung Fu action of the lethal kind when she goes to get the straight scoop from Nick Fury about S.H.I.E.L.D.'s recent ominous doings, and instead runs straight into Razorfist, Shockwave and Zaran!

38.text: After battling Khats, the Doctor’s Cloak of Levitation needs some mending. Cloak of ‘Cloak and Dagger’ meets the ultimate ‘good time bad girl’ in the villainous Ecstasy. Who is Ecstasy, and why is she tormenting Cloak in another cosmos? Doctor Strange must bail out a fellow mystic!

39.text: WILD IN THE STREETS! Prince Namor, aka The Sub-Mariner, has joined The Avengers and the public isn't happy about it! Sensing an opportunity to attack, Moonstone makes her move! Featuring Absorbing Man and Titania.

40.text: When Sam gets anxiety over his girlfriend Lila meeting his mother, he flies off the handle and accuses Lila of being a thief!

41.text: Can X-Factor battle the toxic Glow Worm and Bulk without blowing their cover of being “two” teams?!

57.text: C-3PO & R2-D2 are purchased by Ambassador Zell, who wants the droids to look after his son, Llez, while he's away on business, but the boy feels neglected, and runs away and joins the space pirate Reddjak and his crew, who are using the boy to get to Zell.

58.text: Jakal steals the eldest three Power kids' powers as leverage for Katie!

59.text: Dakota's brother Ricky wins a top-secret technology in a poker game!

61.text: Top Dog meets Heathcliff as they find themselves in the Great Museum Mystery!

62.text:
• Spider-Man Vs. The Horrific Tordenkakerlakk
In The Dimension Of Cloudsea!
•Can Spidey And The Spirited Spindrifter
Overcome A Foe That Becomes More Powerful — And More Terrifying — Each Time It’s Defeated?
•A Macabre Masterpiece Illustrated In Disturbing Detail By Horror Master Bernie Wrightson!
•Reprinting Marvel Graphic Novel #22:
Spider-Man — Hooky.
Fighting against the horrific Tordenkakerlakk, Spider-Man must find a way to overcome a foe that becomes stronger with each defeat.

66.text: The Thing is missing? The search for their newest member puts the West Coast Avengers on a collision course with Headlok!

80.text: Nighthawk's mission is to overthrow the Utopia Program and take the Squadron Supreme out of action. To ensure his plan's success, he sends his agents to infiltrate the Squadron. Will the world's foremost super-team realize before it's too late?

87.text: What is the Kreegon and why has it returned?

88.text: Mr. Power, Cloak, and Franklin Richards are separately on the hunt for the lost Powers kids!

89.text: Tandy and Tyrone are off to France! The super powered duo takes their war on drugs cross continental…and meet a new ally!

90.text: The origins of Master Pandemonium are revealed!

91.text: Enter the Khats! Doctor Strange does battle with brand-new villains whose origins are unknown. One thing Strange does know? Khats are demons possessed...with violence!

94.text: The team comes to the aid of Sue Nowlan when she seeks X-Factor’s help for her ex-husband.

98.text: "Caught In The Quagmire" A hero has died. How will this affect the Squadron Supreme? And in the wake of this great tragedy, the Squadron will have to contend with an extradimensional menace!
